/*
# CSS Reset

Resets the styling of all HTML elements to a consistent baseline.

- all elements with `box-sizing: border-box`
- all elements inherit the `box-sizing`, so no conflicts with external css
- remove `margin` and `padding` in the document, title tags and lists
- images responsive by default

*/
html
  box-sizing border-box
  font-size 16px

*, *:before, *:after
  box-sizing inherit

body, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p, ol, ul
  margin 0
  padding 0
  font-weight normal
  line-height 1

ol, ul
  list-style none

img
  max-width 100%
  height auto
